snippet.title: Sega Saturn - Tenchi Muyou! Toukou Muyou Aniraji Collection (1997) - Intro
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Tenchi Muyou! Toukou Muyou Aniraji Collection is an Adventure game, developed and published by Xing Entertainment, which was released in Japan in 1997.
